These DVD's always drop in price soon after release, which is a great thing. Otherwise, I may not feel they're worth it, but now I get over 20 episodes of one piece for a good price, which really works well with the super-long story arcs of One Piece. The anime, when compared to the manga, definitely is flawed, though. Due to being such a big project, it doesn't have the animation budget it needs, and you can definitely notice that. It may not be for this season particularly, but there's often so much filler that it can take up half a season, which makes it feel like a waste to me. The voice acting on the part of FUNimation is well done though, they rarely disappoint.

In One Piece Collection ten, the straw hat crew reach the city of water seven.  Luffy, Usopp and Nami head into the city of water 7 to find the mayor iceberg. They come to find out the going merry can' be repaired. To make matters worse robin has disappeared, then Luffy and Usopp get in a fight over the going merry. Now CP9 has framed the straw hat crew for the trying to kill the mayor iceberg. So can the straw hat crew figure out what CP9 is up to save the mayor and the city of water seven or will CP9 be the end of the straw hat crew.

One Piece Collection Ten Disc BreakDown

Disc 01.
230. Adventure in the city on the water!-Head to the mammoth shipbuilding plant!
231. The franky family and iceberg.
232. Galley-La company!-A grand sight: dock #1!
233. Pirate abduction incident!-A pirate ship that can only await her end!
234. Rescuing our friend!-Raid on the franky house!
235. Big fight under the moon!-The pirate flag flutters with sorrow!

Disc 02.
236. Luffy vs. Usopp!-Collision of two men's pride!
237. Severe shock hits the city of water!-Iceberg targeted.
238. Gum gum human vs. fire breathing cyborg!
239. The straw hat pirates are the culprits!-The protectors of the city of water!
240. Eternal farewell?-Nico robin: The woman who draws darkness!
241. Capture robin!-The determination of the straw hats!

Disc 03.
242. Cannon fire is the signal!-CP9 goes into action!
243. CP9 Takes off their masks!-Their shocking true faces!
244. Secret bond!-Iceberg and Franky!
245. Come back, Robin!-Showdown with CP9!
246. The straw hat pirates annihilated?-The menace of the leopard model!
247. The man who is loved even by his ship!-Usopp's tears!

Disc 04.
248. Franky's past!-The day the sea train first ran!
249. Spandam's scheme!-The day the sea train shook!
250. The end of the legendary man!-The day the sea train cried!
251. The truth behind her betrayal!-Robin's sorrowful decision!
252. The steam whistle forces friends apart!-The sea train starts to run!

This collection contains Voyages 3 & 4 from season 4 & they're packed with so much set up for what's coming & are just a marvel to watch. Also, it's the intro to Franky & some of Robin's backstory. These episodes are leading to what's coming in the Enies Lobby arc & it's a set that's WAY more worth the money than the Voyages in my opinion. I HIGHLY recommend it to all English-speaking One Piece fans.
